{"tid":1814980,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"一個人都可以示威","createTime":"2020-01-07T07:40:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T01:50:41.000Z","uid":263648,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e88f710f0ef6783d0ab651b0de935c33fed7cfee","tid":1814980,"uid":263648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:40:03.000Z","msg":"公司附近新開咗間Coffee Shop, 成間落地玻璃。總之係紅或藍。你明啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n朝早/lunch, 吸引好多鬼佬幫襯。<br />\n<br />\n隔咗兩日，見到有個西裝友，每朝攞兩張A4, 幾隻英文字，企係Coffee Shop 玻璃外比鬼佬睇。個個鬼佬睇完即刻冇晒Mood。每次都快閃。<br />\n<br />\n我行去八封下，屌，大致意思係：「<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你而家支持緊中國共產黨。呢間係中共企業」</span></span></strong>。今日見少咗好多鬼佬幫襯。<br />\n<br />\n其實<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">抗爭可以係生活的一部分</span></span></strong>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d06c53353abf9bcd7b527f7415b7b1feafc93dd8","tid":1814980,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:51:39.000Z","msg":"一個人武林"},{"pid":"bef7ce8eae60502c6906c367b0741e772b4095a5","tid":1814980,"uid":119810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:52:13.000Z","msg":"RESPECT"},{"pid":"54ecf52b63617169e65b78cb21620882ac8245d7","tid":1814980,"uid":263648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d06c53353abf9bcd7b527f7415b7b1feafc93dd8","tid":1814980,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:51:39.000Z","msg":"一個人武林"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:56:45.000Z","msg":"好多人默默做緊野。我地唔寂寞。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1246280d65791803242605812a75fc8233ceb243","tid":1814980,"uid":263648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bef7ce8eae60502c6906c367b0741e772b4095a5","tid":1814980,"uid":119810,